Question: There is exactly one cat that is entirely black.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/80/be/03/80be037943d5bc71b1ccb1fe0f1b59f9.jpg

Right image URL: http://kittentoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/page.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many cats are entirely black?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many cats are entirely black?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} + {ANSWER1} == 1')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
